Package net.minecraft.network.protocol

Interface Packet<T extends net.minecraft.network.PacketListener>

Type Parameters:
T - The packet listener type that can process this packet.
public interface Packet<T extends net.minecraft.network.PacketListener> 
Represents an abstract Packet type. All packet objects descend from this interface.
